OL,3,CWomb transplants: How do they work and
OL,4,Cwill they become more common?
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Hannah Ward-
OL,7,FGlenton
OL,9,FA baby boy has become the first child
OL,10,Fin the UK to be born to a mother who
OL,11,Freceived a womb from a donor who had
OL,12,Fdied.
OL,14,FBaby Hugo was delivered weighing 6lb
OL,15,F13oz in December at Queen Charlotte's
OL,16,Fand Chelsea Hospital, part of Imperial
OL,17,FCollege Healthcare NHS Trust.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
