OL,3,CWomb transplants: How do they work and
OL,4,Cwill they become more common?
OL,6,FThere are two types of womb
OL,7,Ftransplants: it can be done from a
OL,8,Fliving woman or from a woman who has
OL,9,Fdied and had already consented to
OL,10,Fdonating her womb.
OL,12,FThe womb is not covered by the normal
OL,13,Fconsent for donation, nor by joining
OL,14,Fthe organ donor register, and it is
OL,15,Fnot covered by deemed consent (which
OL,16,Fpresumes people want to donate unless
OL,17,Fthey opt out).
OL,19,FEach case might be slightly different
OL,20,Fdue to variations in the women.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
