OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771956278
OL,3,CWomb transplants: How do they work and
OL,4,Cwill they become more common?
OL,6,FGrace Davidson, for example, underwent
OL,7,Ffertility treatment to create seven
OL,8,Fembryos, which were then frozen for
OL,9,FIVF.
OL,11,FShe then had surgery to receive a womb
OL,12,Ffrom her sister Amy, and several
OL,13,Fmonths later, one of the stored
OL,14,Fembryos was transferred to Grace via
OL,15,FIVF. She carried the baby to term and
OL,16,Fgave birth by Cesarean section.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
