OL,3,CWomb transplants: How do they work and
OL,4,Cwill they become more common?
OL,6,FWomb transplants come with the same
OL,7,Frisks associated with other non-life-
OL,8,Fsaving transplant procedures.
OL,10,FThe surgery is also a long procedure -
OL,11,Fin the case of Grace Bell, Hugo's mum,
OL,12,Fit lasted 10 hours - and so carries
OL,13,Fthe risks associated with lengthy
OL,14,Fsurgery procedures.
OL,16,FWhy is a womb transplant necessary?
OL,18,FOne in 5,000 women in the UK is born
OL,19,Fwithout a womb, leaving them unable to
OL,20,Fconceive and carry a child without any
OL,21,Fmedical intervention.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
