OL,3,CWomb transplants: How do they work and
OL,4,Cwill they become more common?
OL,6,FIs giving birth the same after a womb
OL,7,Ftransplant?
OL,9,FAll known womb transplants so far have
OL,10,Fresulted in births by Cesarean section
OL,11,Frather than vaginal births.
OL,13,FC-sections are considered much safer
OL,14,Ffollowing a womb transplant because of
OL,15,Fbiological differences caused by the
OL,16,Fprocedure, such as the fact that there
OL,17,Fare no contractions during the
OL,18,Fpregnancy or labour.
OL,20,FWho pays for the transplants?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
