OL,3,CWomb transplants: How do they work and
OL,4,Cwill they become more common?
OL,6,FWomb Transplant UK currently raises
OL,7,Ffunds for the research and procedures
OL,8,Finvolved in womb transplants, and it
OL,9,Fis not funded by the NHS.
OL,11,FWill womb transplants become more
OL,12,Fcommon?
OL,14,FHugo and Amy's successful births give
OL,15,Fhope to women without a womb or whose
OL,16,Fwomb works differently than what is
OL,17,Fneeded to sustain a pregnancy.
OL,19,FWomb Transplant UK has plans for more
OL,20,Fsimilar surgeries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
