OL,3,CWomb transplants: How do they work and
OL,4,Cwill they become more common?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIt hopes to complete 10 operations
OL,12,Ftransplanting a womb from a brain-dead
OL,13,Fdonor - the first having been baby
OL,14,FHugo - and five operations
OL,15,Ftransplanting a womb from a living
OL,16,Frelative of the recipient, the first
OL,17,Fof which was baby Amy in April 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
