OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1771956278
OL,3,CWomb transplants: How do they work and
OL,4,Cwill they become more common?
OL,6,FThe lead surgeons for the womb
OL,7,Ftransplants were Professor Richard
OL,8,FSmith, clinical lead at the charity
OL,9,FWomb Transplant UK and consultant
OL,10,Fgynaecological surgeon at Imperial
OL,11,FCollege Healthcare NHS Trust, and Dr
OL,12,FIsabel Quiroga, consultant surgeon at
OL,13,Fthe Oxford Transplant Centre, part of
OL,14,FOxford University Hospitals.
OL,16,FBoth have worked on womb transplant
OL,17,Fresearch for decades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
